passages.text: CSI300 gained \(2.7\%\) on record volumes and outperformed MSCI China \((- 0.8\%)\) . We expect the liquidity- driven rally in A shares to extend and raise our CSI300 12- month index target to 4900. CPPCC National Committee held the 13th session to draft the country's 15th Five- Year Plan. The State Council issued opinions to deepen the implementation of the "Artificial Intelligence+" action plan. The Ministry of Commerce looked to expand inbound consumption and increase support for foreign trade enterprises. The State Administration for Market Regulation held a meeting to promote comprehensive rectification of market competition order and prevent irrational competition. Our economists expect the NBS manufacturing PMI to stay flat and services PMI to increase in August. \(84\% /70\%\) of all China listed/MSCI China universe has reported so far with 1H25 earnings rising \(5\% /3\%\) yoy.

H: Materials \((9.5\%)\) & Growth \((7.8\%)\) outperformed, while Real Estate \((4.4\%)\) & Value \((- 6.0\%)\) lagged A- share: Materials \((3.5\%)\) & Growth \((5.5\%)\) outperformed, while Energy \((- 5.6\%)\) & Value \((- 4.7\%)\) lagged
MXC/N/CSI300 12m forward P/Es are 12.6x/14.5x I/B/E/S consensus 2025/26E EPS growth is \(5\% /14\%\) and \(15\% /13\%\) for MXCN and CSI300, respectively Health Care was revised up the most
The State Council released opinions on promoting high- quality urban development.
